  <description><![CDATA[<p>An opportunity to see contrasting areas of lovely <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> with this 2 centre holiday with included excursions.  Arrive on Wednesday and spend 3 nights right in the centre of historic Como town with its famous Gothic cathedral and characterful cobbled streets. While in the city of <a data-udi="umb://document/a466e45e88084c09a318aa7ecdfde7d4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a466e45e88084c09a318aa7ecdfde7d4}" title="Como">Como</a> you might like to take the train into cosmopolitan Milan for the day, with its famous sights and endless shopping possibilities or take a boat ride on Lake Como to nearby Cernobbio or other pretty town.  On Saturday transfer by ferry to <a data-udi="umb://document/80beb49bbb7f416ba46131e7c79367b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/80beb49bbb7f416ba46131e7c79367b5}" title="Menaggio">Menaggio</a> for 7 nights staying in a hotel on the lakeside.  Enjoy an included excursion to St Moritz which features a train ride on the world famous Bernina Express and also an excursion to the historic medieval city of Bergamo. In Como Inghams representatives will give you some information to help you get around and will be contactable by phone. In Menaggio, Inghams Representatives will be on hand to advise and assist and help you enjoy your holiday to the full.</p>
<p> </p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 50px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
