</table>
</div>
<div> </div>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Itinerary</strong></p>
<p><strong>Day 1: Wednesday</strong><br />Transfer by coach from the airport to the Hotel Barchetta Excelsior in Como.</p>
<p><strong>Days 2/3: Thursday &amp; Friday </strong><br />Free days to explore the city of Como. Visit the amazing Gothic cathedral, explore the city and enjoy its many restaurants and bars. Take a train to busy, bustling <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a> or take a boat trip on the lake to one of the nearby resorts.</p>
<p><strong>Day 4: Saturday<br /></strong>Transfer by ferry from the ferry terminal close to your hotel in Como and disembark in Menaggio right beside the Grand Hotel Menaggio where you will stay for 7 nights.</p>
<p><strong>Day 5: Sunday</strong><br />Your first day in Menaggio where you can relax and enjoy getting to know the local area. </p>
<p><strong>Day 6: Monday</strong><br /><strong>St Moritz and the Bernina Express Excursion</strong> - travel to Switzerland for a memorable day to glitzy St Moritz and the wonderful Bernina Express train ride from Poschiavo.</p>
<p><strong>Days <strong>7/8: </strong>Tuesday &amp; Wednesday<br /></strong>Free days to explore Lake Como - take a ferry ride to picturesque Bellagio, visit the famous Villa Carlotta which is in nearby <a data-udi="umb://document/cdc14b14dbcd46c6bb2d675f73a3a375" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cdc14b14dbcd46c6bb2d675f73a3a375}" title="Tremezzo">Tremezzo</a> or relax by the pool in your hotel.<strong><br /></strong></p>
<p><strong>Day 9: Thursday</strong><br />Bergamo Excursion - Enjoy a guided visit to one of Italy's most impressive medieval cities. The cost of the ferry ticket to the pick up point in Varenna is not included (approx. €8 return).</p>
<p><strong>Day 10: Friday</strong><br />A final day to take in some sunshine and enjoy the beautiful lake.</p>
<p><strong>Day 11: Saturday</strong><br />Transfer to the airport for your flight home.</p>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure dates &amp; prices</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>• Flights depart Wednesday from 29 May - 18 Sep 2019</li>
<li>• Prices from £1,479 per person based on 2 adults</li>
<li>• Room upgrades and single/sole occupancy rooms are available at a supplement</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>What’s included</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>• Return flights to Milan from the UK on Wednesday, returning Saturday</li>
<li>• Transfers by coach between the airport and your hotels</li>
<li>• Transfers between Como and Menaggio</li>
<li>• 10 nights accommodation in 4 star hotels (mixed board basis)</li>
<li>• 2 full day excursions to St Moritz and Bergamo</li>
<li>• Assistance of Inghams Reps in Menaggio and telephone contact when in Como</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Your Hotels</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>• Como <em>(3 nights only)</em></strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/119873a5de764e63a6bcb57efc575c47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/119873a5de764e63a6bcb57efc575c47}" title="Hotel Barchetta">Hotel Barchetta Excelsior</a> ****</li>
<li><strong>• Menaggio <em>(7 nights)</em></strong>  <a data-udi="umb://document/ed3168e942f6443c8c29582c01c0cd4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed3168e942f6443c8c29582c01c0cd4d}" title="Grand Hotel Menaggio">Grand Hotel Menaggio</a> ****</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure flights to Milan from:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>• Gatwick, Heathrow, Stansted, Luton</li>
<li>• Birmingham, Manchester &amp; Edinburgh</li>
<li>• Flight supplements may apply</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
